snippet.title: Gunfire Reborn | gamescom Co-Op Trailer
snippet.description: Gunfire Reborn, the hit first-person roguelike game, is coming to Xbox Game Pass on October 27th! Fight your way through randomized levels, battle hordes of enemies, grab the loot and level up your heroes! It’s non-stop action with endless replayablity.
